38:16.859 --> 38:18.383
-♪ "L"♪
-I thought you wanted it.

38:18.426 --> 38:20.341
♪ Is for the way you look♪

38:20.385 --> 38:22.604
-I thought...
-♪ At me♪

38:22.648 --> 38:29.045
♪ "O" is for the only one
I see...♪

38:29.089 --> 38:32.353
Fuck me now or I'll kill you.

38:32.397 --> 38:33.963
