poured tea in my lap.

41:56.252 --> 41:58.124
There is

41:58.167 --> 42:00.605
an accelerating forgetfulness.

42:00.648 --> 42:04.783
Understandable
as time takes its toll.

42:04.826 --> 42:07.960
